\begin_inset Formula $\KET{\psi}$
\end_inset

 is then defined as:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\norm{\psi}:=\norm{\KET{\psi}} & :=\sqrt{\left\langle \psi,\psi\right\rangle }
\end{align*}

\end_inset

If 
\begin_inset Formula $\norm{\KET{\psi}}=1$
